6469e21;Jeff Forcier;2009-09-09 15:44:54 -0400;Reorder contains(), append() args for consistency.
This is a backwards compatible API change. Previously, contains() and
append() had arg specs of func(text, filename, ...) -- they now mirror
all other contrib.files.* functions and have arg specs of func(filename,
text, ...).

