INSTALL
==================
3cd3f52;Jeff Forcier;2009-05-05 19:39:53 -0400;Merge shell/shell_args back together -- it really should be one string.
Rationale:
* Args are almost always specific to a given shell;
* Users not aware of the split may override shell but not shell_args;

Thanks to karmazilla and alisaifee for the feedback.

