ddc9b99;Jeff Forcier;2008-12-30 10:52:21 -0500;Undo 80-col tweak -- long strings are the one exception to the rule :)
IMO, splitting and joining strings just to avoid line breaks is less readable.
Makes readers go "wait why is that string being joined..." before they realize
it's just to avoid the linebreak. Not worth it :)

