README
fab
==================
c3a582e;Christian Vest Hansen;2008-01-05 17:50:07 +0100;Lots of polish and bug fixes.
- error checking on the paramiko import now only catches ImportErrors.
- add variable to configure how new host keys are handled. Default is accept, anything else rejects.
- impl. local_per_host operation and fix the syntax error it posed.
- impl. command specific help, such as $fab help:list will display help msg. for the list cmd.
- output of list command is now sorted by cmd name.
- add set command to set variables from the CLI.
- if no command is given on CLI, complain and run list.
- remember to close the connections to the servers once we've done our job.
- don't print SystemExit traces if some internal function want's to quit.
- fabfile.example had the docstring in the wrong place in the tail and restart command.

==

